pinnochio and his father lived in a very poor house. His father worked as a tradesman. Once, when pinnochio was walking down a street,
he was very hingry. So he decided to buy a box of sweets for him. He saw an old woman walking down the street who was begging for food. 
When she came to him, he lied that he carried a box of papers.
The woman turned out to be a magic fairy.